== dhandlers

* dhandlers create virtual URLs.
+* Make a request for _/view/files/id-1.html_.
** but there is no such component.
+* Mason looks for _/view/files/dhandler_ ...
** ... then _/view/dhandler_ ...
** ... and finally _/dhandler_.

