== Caching

* Integration with [=Cache::Cache] is built-in.
* You can cache anything:

    $m->cache->set( $key => $value, $expiration );

+* But the coolest part is caching a component's output:

.hilite
<%init>
return if $m->cache_self($key);

...
</%init>

<h1>Statistics</h1>

