== Blocks

* Most blocks contain pure Perl.
** but how the Perl is used depends on the block.
* The pure Perl blocks are [=<%perl>], [=<%init>], [=<%once>], [=<%filter>], [=<%shared>], and [=<%cleanup>].

----------------------------------------------

